{"tid":266913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黑肥童年！陳建州兒時照「飛翔」看傻眼","createTime":"2017-06-02T00:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T03:58:35.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ea44b8a9e10989d1af5c2e8d615e0f285f0367","tid":266913,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-01/590/20170601002398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-01%2F590%2F20170601002398.jpg&h=0a40db3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑人兒時的照片，飛翔也看傻眼？（圖／取自黑人臉書）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-01/656/20170601002403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-01%2F656%2F20170601002403.jpg&h=7a790c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑人熱愛運動後，現在是個超級帥爸。（圖／本報系資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n「黑人」陳建州和「范范」范瑋琪婚後育有一對雙胞胎「飛飛」、「翔翔」，平時夫妻倆最愛和粉絲在網上分享天倫樂，不過黑人昨則是曬出自己的兒時照，不同於其他藝人超Q模樣，小時候的黑人可說是又黑又胖，黑人不忘合成一張「飛翔」看到他「暗黑童年」的驚訝照。<br />\n<br />\n陳建州昨貼出兒時照，照片的他又黑又胖，和現在的模樣差很大，他也自嘲「記得當時年紀小」，但後來身高抽高、黑人也迷上健身與運動，瘦成現在的高挑帥男；不過黑人不忘搞怪，貼出一張「飛翔」看到老爸兒時胖黑的傻眼照，還有人搞笑稱「飛翔怕變成老爸這樣？」超級逗趣。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170601002376-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170601002376-260404&d=88oHizLfb6OmYZ3Fk6n5jp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=49485136\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170601002376-260404</a>"},{"pid":"90a4cf6849ccadc71cd0bf22f6504c2b8fae9e0f","tid":266913,"uid":46086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:07:12.000Z","msg":"not interested"},{"pid":"b82f6c84ede157472e15522c377f9f8e08e46edd","tid":266913,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0267aa6b72d65fddcea9fe1197b697d7bd507bad","tid":266913,"uid":29826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},{"pid":"8522eb4de311ef531f0862e920459b6c1a38c1bd","tid":266913,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"煩膠夫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e5d438e76b44f6436af62b1f2496fe46e968f8","tid":266913,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"帥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}